Comment.val: /*Creates an export file for the given range. The file contains data to check wheter or not the TOSA calculation is correct.*/
/*Report Only Processed records (P), Only Non Processed records (N),Both proccessed and non processed (B), Base amount below threshold (T) or All records (A)*/

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT a.reference_date "REF_DATE", SUM(a.total_amount_product_syst_curr) "TOTAL_PRODUCT", SUM(a.total_blocked_amt_syst_curr) "TOTAL_BLOCKED", SUM(a.total_nominative_amt_syst_curr) "TOTAL_NOMINATIVE" FROM tosa_amounts_per_product a INNER JOIN tosa_calc_products p ON p.id = a.tcp_id WHERE p.tch_id = ~1 GROUP BY a.reference_date ORDER BY a.reference_date
